<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" ?>
<Defs>

	<ThingDef ParentName="NonDeconstructibleAncientBuildingBase">
		<defName>Building_Ancient_WarBeacon</defName>
		<label>破碎的信标旧址</label>
		<description>这座战争信标早已饱经战火的洗礼，残垣断壁诉说着一场惨烈的过往。尽管其表面伤痕累累、结构破碎，但核心框架依旧坚固如初，仿佛静静等待着重返战场的那一刻。
如果你能筹集足够的资源并完成修复，或许就能再次唤醒它沉睡的力量——将其重构为真正的战争信标，点燃机械族对这片土地的关注，也为你带来前所未有的科技突破。
它静候着……是重启，还是遗忘？</description>
		<thingClass>NCL.Building_Ancient_WarBeacon</thingClass>
		<drawerType>MapMeshAndRealTime</drawerType>
    <graphicData>
      <texPath>Buildings/AncientWarBeacon</texPath>
      <graphicClass>Graphic_Multi</graphicClass>
      <shadowData>
        <volume>(1.1, 0.75, 1.1)</volume>
      </shadowData>
    </graphicData>
	    <uiIconPath>Buildings/AncientWarBeaconUI</uiIconPath>
		<altitudeLayer>MoteOverhead</altitudeLayer>
		<passability>PassThroughOnly</passability>
		<fillPercent>0.45</fillPercent>
		<pathCost>42</pathCost>
		<destroyable>true</destroyable>
        <useHitPoints>false</useHitPoints>
		<statBases>
			<WorkToBuild>600</WorkToBuild>
			<Mass>10</Mass>
			<Flammability>0</Flammability>
		</statBases>
		<size>(3,3)</size>
		<costList>
			<Steel>10</Steel>
			<WoodLog>30</WoodLog>
		</costList>
		<tickerType>Rare</tickerType>
		<rotatable>true</rotatable>
		<constructEffect>ConstructWood</constructEffect>
		<building>
     <alwaysDeconstructible>false</alwaysDeconstructible>
			<deconstructible>false</deconstructible>
			<destroySound>BuildingDestroyed_Wood_Small</destroySound>
		</building>
    <comps>
      <li Class="CompProperties_ProximityLetter">
        <radius>4</radius>
        <letterDef>PositiveEvent</letterDef>
        <letterLabel>破碎的信标旧址</letterLabel>
        <letterText>这座战争信标早已饱经战火的洗礼，残垣断壁诉说着一场惨烈的过往。尽管其表面伤痕累累、结构破碎，但核心框架依旧坚固如初，仿佛静静等待着重返战场的那一刻。
如果你能筹集足够的资源并完成修复，或许就能再次唤醒它沉睡的力量——将其重构为真正的战争信标，点燃机械族对这片土地的关注，也为你带来前所未有的科技突破。
它静候着……是重启，还是遗忘？</letterText>
      </li>
    </comps>
		<modExtensions>
			<li Class="NCL.ModExtension_AncientWarBeacon">
				<finalThing>Building_TotalWarfareActivator</finalThing>
				<toggleGizmoIcon>ModIcon/FixingTheBuilding</toggleGizmoIcon>
                <toggleGizmoOffIcon>ModIcon/NotFixingTheBuilding</toggleGizmoOffIcon>
				<stages>
					<li>
						<Things>
							<Steel>250</Steel>
							<SignalChip>1</SignalChip>
							<ComponentSpacer>2</ComponentSpacer>
							<ComponentIndustrial>4</ComponentIndustrial>
						</Things>
						<Rewards>
						</Rewards>
						<graphic>
                           <texPath>Buildings/AncientWarBeacon</texPath>
                           <graphicClass>Graphic_Multi</graphicClass>
                           <drawSize>(6,6)</drawSize>
                           <shadowData>
                           <volume>(1.1, 0.75, 1.1)</volume>
                           </shadowData>
						</graphic>

					</li>
				</stages>
			</li>
		</modExtensions>
	</ThingDef>
	
	<WorkGiverDef>
		<defName>WorkGiver_RebuildTheWarBeacon</defName>
		<label>修复破损建筑</label>
		<giverClass>NCL.WorkGiver_RebuildTheWarBeacon</giverClass>
		<workType>Hauling</workType>
		<verb>fill</verb>
		<gerund>filling</gerund>
		<priorityInType>114</priorityInType>
		<requiredCapacities>
			<li>Manipulation</li>
		</requiredCapacities>
		<canBeDoneByMechs>false</canBeDoneByMechs>
	</WorkGiverDef>
	
		<JobDef>
		<defName>RebuildTheWarBeacon</defName>
		<driverClass>NCL.JobDriver_RebuildTheWarBeacon</driverClass>
		<reportString>修复 TargetA.</reportString>
		<suspendable>false</suspendable>
		<allowOpportunisticPrefix>true</allowOpportunisticPrefix>
	</JobDef>
	
	<ThingDef ParentName="NonDeconstructibleAncientBuildingBase">
    <defName>Building_TotalWarfareActivator</defName>
    <label>战争信标</label>
	<thingClass>NCL.Building_TotalWarfareActivator</thingClass>
    <description>你已成功修复这座战争信标，它庞大的构造在废土之上仿佛一尊沉眠的巨兽，令人不寒而栗。作为机械族用以标定战略坐标的核心建筑，它的激活意味着你将暴露于他们的视野之中——更强大、更致命的机械部队将陆续涌来，妄图将你彻底摧毁。
但高风险亦伴随高回报。通过分析信标的核心数据，你有望破解机械族的技术壁垒，解锁曾经遥不可及的尖端科技。
选择权在你手中——是沉默以保全，还是点燃战火，直面未知？
打开它，打开战争。</description>
    <graphicData>
      <texPath>Buildings/CompleteWarBeacon</texPath>
      <graphicClass>Graphic_Multi</graphicClass>
      <drawSize>(6,6)</drawSize>
      <shadowData>
        <volume>(1.1, 0.75, 1.1)</volume>
      </shadowData>
    </graphicData>
	<uiIconPath>Buildings/WarBeaconUI</uiIconPath>
    <altitudeLayer>MoteOverhead</altitudeLayer>
    <passability>PassThroughOnly</passability>
    <fillPercent>0.3</fillPercent>
    <useHitPoints>false</useHitPoints>
    <building>
     <alwaysDeconstructible>false</alwaysDeconstructible>
      <ai_chillDestination>false</ai_chillDestination>
      <buildingTags>
        <li>Biotech</li>
      </buildingTags>
    </building>
    <uiOrder>2460</uiOrder>
    <statBases>
      <WorkToBuild>8000</WorkToBuild>
      <Mass>25</Mass>
      <Flammability>0</Flammability>
    </statBases>
    <size>(3,3)</size>
    <killedLeavings>
      <ChunkSlagSteel>5</ChunkSlagSteel>
	  <TW_Precision_Memory_Interface_Array>1</TW_Precision_Memory_Interface_Array>
    </killedLeavings>
    <comps>
      <li Class="CompProperties_Usable">
        <useJob>TriggerObject</useJob>
        <useLabel>开启全面战争X</useLabel>
        <useDuration>900</useDuration>
        <floatMenuFactionIcon>Mechanoid</floatMenuFactionIcon>
      </li>
	  <li Class="NCL.CompProperties_UseEffect_ActivateWarfare">
      <activateEffect>MechbandBuildingDestroyed</activateEffect>
      <delayTicks>120</delayTicks> <!-- 2秒延迟 -->
    </li>
      <li Class="CompProperties_UseEffectDestroySelf">
        <delayTicks>120</delayTicks>
        <spawnKilledLeavings>true</spawnKilledLeavings>
        <effecterDef>MechbandDishUsed</effecterDef>
      </li>
	<li Class="CompProperties_UseEffectPlaySound">
        <soundOnUsed>CommsConsoleBossgroupSummoned</soundOnUsed>
      </li>
    </comps>
    <tickerType>Normal</tickerType>
    <filthLeaving>Filth_MachineBits</filthLeaving>
  </ThingDef>
  
    <ThingDef ParentName="NonDeconstructibleAncientBuildingBase">
    <defName>Ancient_WarBeacon_PartsA</defName>
    <label>破碎信标碎片</label>
    <description>战争信标残骸中散落的组件碎片，其内部结构已严重损毁，不具备任何战术或通讯功能。但对于资源短缺的殖民地来说，这些碎片依旧可作为金属与复合材料的来源。</description>
    <rotatable>true</rotatable>
    <graphicData>
      <texPath>Buildings/AncientWarBeaconAParts</texPath>
      <graphicClass>Graphic_Single</graphicClass>
      <drawSize>(2,2)</drawSize>
      <shadowData>
        <volume>(1, 1, 0.4)</volume>
        <offset>(-0.2,0,-0.2)</offset>
      </shadowData>
    </graphicData>
    <size>(2,1)</size>
    <fillPercent>0.5</fillPercent>
    <passability>PassThroughOnly</passability>
    <pathCost>50</pathCost>
    <statBases>
      <MaxHitPoints>1000</MaxHitPoints>
    </statBases>
    <killedLeavings>
      <Plasteel>150</Plasteel>
      <ComponentIndustrial>5</ComponentIndustrial>
    </killedLeavings>
  </ThingDef>
  
      <ThingDef ParentName="NonDeconstructibleAncientBuildingBase">
    <defName>Ancient_WarBeacon_PartsB</defName>
    <label>破碎信标碎片</label>
    <description>战争信标残骸中散落的组件碎片，其内部结构已严重损毁，不具备任何战术或通讯功能。但对于资源短缺的殖民地来说，这些碎片依旧可作为金属与复合材料的来源。</description>
    <rotatable>true</rotatable>
    <graphicData>
      <texPath>Buildings/AncientWarBeaconBParts</texPath>
      <graphicClass>Graphic_Single</graphicClass>
      <drawSize>(2,2)</drawSize>
      <shadowData>
        <volume>(1, 1, 0.4)</volume>
        <offset>(-0.2,0,-0.2)</offset>
      </shadowData>
    </graphicData>
    <size>(2,1)</size>
    <fillPercent>0.5</fillPercent>
    <passability>PassThroughOnly</passability>
    <pathCost>50</pathCost>
    <statBases>
      <MaxHitPoints>1000</MaxHitPoints>
    </statBases>
    <killedLeavings>
      <Plasteel>150</Plasteel>
      <ComponentIndustrial>5</ComponentIndustrial>
    </killedLeavings>
  </ThingDef>

    <ThingDef ParentName="NonDeconstructibleAncientBuildingBase">
    <defName>Broken_War_Scorpion_Rust</defName>
    <label>战争巨蝎残骸</label>
    <description>一只战争巨蝎的残骸,你感受到其中似乎存在某些有价值的事物</description>
    <thingClass>Building</thingClass>
    <rotatable>false</rotatable>
    <graphicData>
      <texPath>Buildings/BrokenWarScorpionRust</texPath>
      <graphicClass>Graphic_Single</graphicClass>
      <drawSize>(4,4)</drawSize>
      <shadowData>
        <volume>(1, 1, 1)</volume>
        <offset>(-0.2,0,-0.2)</offset>
      </shadowData>
    </graphicData>
    <size>(3,3)</size>
    <fillPercent>0.5</fillPercent>
    <passability>PassThroughOnly</passability>
    <pathCost>50</pathCost>
    <statBases>
      <MaxHitPoints>3000</MaxHitPoints>
    </statBases>
    <building>
     <alwaysDeconstructible>false</alwaysDeconstructible>
			<deconstructible>false</deconstructible>
    </building>
    <killedLeavings>
      <Uranium>75</Uranium>
      <Plasteel>50</Plasteel>
      <Steel>150</Steel>
      <NCL_RedCube>1</NCL_RedCube>
    </killedLeavings>
    <comps>
      <li Class="CompProperties_Glower">
        <glowRadius>3</glowRadius>
        <glowColor>(200, 0, 0, 0)</glowColor>
      </li>
      <li Class="CompProperties_ProximityLetter">
        <radius>4</radius>
        <letterDef>PositiveEvent</letterDef>
        <letterLabel>战争巨蝎残骸</letterLabel>
        <letterText>当你靠近这座战争巨蝎残骸时,你感受到其中似乎存在某些有价值的事物,你隐隐约约看到其头部的一块闪闪发光的红色立方体,也许其能提取出为你所用</letterText>
      </li>
      <li Class="CompProperties_LeavingsLetter">
        <letterLabel>可用的: {LEAVINGS1_label}</letterLabel>
        <letterText>战争巨蝎残骸毁坏后留下了一份红色魔方,也许你能用它解锁什么科技</letterText>
        <letterDef>PositiveEvent</letterDef>
        <leavingsFilter>
          <thingDefs>
            <li>NCL_RedCube</li>
          </thingDefs>
        </leavingsFilter>
      </li>
      <li Class="CompProperties_InspectString">
        <inspectString>包含一块闪闪发光的红色立方体.</inspectString>
      </li>
    </comps>
    <tickerType>Normal</tickerType>
  </ThingDef>

</Defs>